; Metadata-seeding fixture for the [Scanner][Metadata] tests: date,
; two *team lines (joined with ", "), and a declination. The set
; declination also makes this the file-owns-declination fixture for
; the [Attach][Declination] driver-emission tests.
*begin WithMetadata
*date 2025-06-01
*team Alice
*team Bob
*calibrate declination 7.2
*fix A1 0 0 0
*data normal from to tape compass clino
A1 A2 10.0 0 0
*end WithMetadata
